<li><a name="fifty8">Dulude,</a> <i>supra</i> note 3 at 88, citing Thorson, &quot;An Analysis of the Sources of Continued Controversy over the Tax Treatment of Family Income&quot; (1965) 18 Nat'l Tax J. 113 at 116.
<p>
<li><a name="fifty9">Maloney, <i>supra</i> note 3 at 188.</a>
