<li><a name="sixty">J.B. Davies,</a> &quot;The Tax Treatment of the Family&quot; in R.M. Bird &amp; J.M. Mintz, eds., <cite>Taxation to 2000 and Beyond</cite>, (Toronto: Canadian Tax Foundation, 1992) 166 at 169--170.
<p>
<li><a name="sixty1">Dulude,</a> <i>supra</i> note 3 at 88--89 citing J. Pahl, &quot;Patterns of Money Management Within Marriage&quot; (1980) 9 J. of Soc. Pol. at 313.
