<li><a name="one39">Such a separation furthers the policies of certainty</a> and predictability. To ensure that the judiciary interprets and implements legislation in the manner intended, the legislature will craft its enactments to maximize their precision. The separation thus deters vagueness in the conduct of the legislative branch, thereby giving an individual actor greater certainty as to its legal rights and duties.
